Project: AGMS (FE React + BE .NET Web API) - Clean Architecture 4 layers

Rules:
- Domain: chỉ chứa Entities/ValueObjects/Enums/Domain logic. KHÔNG EF Core, KHÔNG Http, KHÔNG DI.
- Application: Use cases (Commands/Queries/Handlers), DTOs, Interfaces. KHÔNG EF Core DbContext.
- Infrastructure: EF Core DbContext, Repositories implement interfaces, external services adapters.
- WebApi: Controllers/Endpoints, DI wiring, Swagger/CORS/Auth. Controller chỉ gọi Application (MediatR/service), không viết business logic nặng.

When generating code:
- Always propose file paths to create/modify before writing code.
- Keep changes minimal and compile-ready.
- Update DI registration when adding new services.
- For APIs: use REST naming, return proper status codes.
